<!DOCTYPE html>

<html>
  <head>
    <style>
	  html {
  	  	background-image: url(https://mobimg.b-cdn.net/v3/fetch/78/783fcb1399e9d4552bdabf6287498373.jpeg);
	  	background-repeat: no-repeat;
	  	background-position: center center;
	  	background-attachment: fixed;
	  	-webkit-background-size: cover;
	  	-moz-background-size: cover;
	  	-o-background-size: cover;
	  	background-size: cover;
	  }
	  
	  h1 {
	    font-family: Phosphate;
	    font-size: 36px;
	    color: white;
	    text-align: center;
	  }
	  
	  .button {
  	  text-decoration: none;
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 15px 30px;
      margin: 10px 20px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 40px 40px #32dae3 inset, 0 0 0 0 #32dae3;
      font-family: Phosphate;
      font-weight: bold;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
      color: white;
      transition: .15s ease-in-out;
      font-size: 30px;
    }
	.button:hover {
	  background-color: white;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px 0 #32dae3 inset, 0 0 10px 4px #32dae3;
      color: #32dae3;
    }
    
    form {
      text-align: center;
    }
	</style>
	<title>Choose_Food</title>
	<meta charset="UTF-8">
  </head>
  
  <body>
    <h1>Яку саме їжу ти хочеш дати?</h1>
